Between the end of 2014 and early 2015, 9 year old B.S.N. and 11 year old P.S.P. were raped multiple times by 17 year old suspect Mr. Vorn Kong. Both victims were from Kesdong village, Kang Cham commune, Thalaborivath district, Stung Treng province. 
After brining their case to ADHOC, the ADHOC provincial team was able to intervene and bring the case to the provincial police. The 17 year old suspect was arrested by the police and is being questioned at the provincial court.
ADHOC will keep following up this case to make sure justice is served.